{"tid":230201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要買樓唔租樓，呢張單可以話到俾你知","createTime":"2017-05-05T07:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T09:24:35.000Z","uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9d5c71c2df18d5e32286c2d3220385f5b05805","tid":230201,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/152851_732266802e1e51d9b7594d4346480500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F152851_732266802e1e51d9b7594d4346480500.jpg&h=368a050a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n收到銀寄黎嘅通知書，啲人又話加息，點知通知我修訂後減左息<br />\n不過呢個唔係重點，重點係去到最後一期還款，2045年11月26日，都只係同今日差唔多，如果租樓，我唔知會被加租幾多囉，到時可能因為通賬每月用3，4萬交租，2045年時1萬4一個月，房署嘅公屋都唔知租唔租到喇，點解啲人唔識計數"},{"pid":"8f7d45b438d68557aa974f729f8cb7a088df9770","tid":230201,"uid":112494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:55:12.000Z","msg":"供完之後住左2年 2047年 地契失效 中共正式接管香港 你都係要去輪公屋"},{"pid":"6cce26ea998be8cb426f2d0f18778bd5fb644442","tid":230201,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:56:49.000Z","msg":"果個預計黎嫁on9"},{"pid":"e0e1c515a55b12366deff291241e7c3ac1c846d0","tid":230201,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3587e4d4ab096bb2179d8a501a6ea7c0615507e","tid":230201,"uid":112494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>供完之後住左2年 2047年 地契失效 中共正式接管香港 你都係要去輪公屋</blockquote><br />\n咁都可以慳兩年租金　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點知呢兩年入面 又外牆維修 又壞升降機 我真係恭喜你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到時望番住呢張野問自己點解當初唔租樓"},{"pid":"2017429538e9df895bfe9cca791702394aeeb6b2","tid":230201,"uid":9796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:59:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquot